To calculate the LIX readability score, we will use the following formula:

LIX = (P * 0.194) + (B * 0.45) + (G * 0.0786)

Where:
- P is the percentage of long words (7+ characters) per total words
- B is the percentage of words per sentence
- G is the percentage of words longer than 7 characters

